/* Table: "CON_YearDiscountSituation" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_YearDiscountSituation"
(
"DiscountSituationID" INTEGER not null,
"MallID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"MallCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"BudgetarTotal" NUMBER(10,2) default 0 not null,
"OutlookTotal" NUMBER(10,2) default 0 not null,
"OutlookBudgetarDiffe" NUMBER(10,2) default 0 not null,
"DiscountTotal" NUMBER(10,2) default 0 not null,
"BeenDiscountTotal" NUMBER(10,2) default 0 not null,
"AvailableDiscountTotal" NUMBER(10,2) default 0 not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
constraint PK_CON_YEARDISCOUNTSITUATION primary key ("DiscountSituationID")
);

comment on column "CON_YearDiscountSituation"."Enable" is
'1:有效
0：无效';
